                      Decorative designs:
                      <locus target = "#1r"/> (<foreign xml:lang = "gez">ሐረግ፡</foreign> with red and black ink);
                      <locus target = "#21v #26r #63r #77v #79v"/>, (rows of full-stop symbols, some with interspersed lines of alternating red and black dots);
                      <locus target = "#69r"/> (row of alternating red and black dots);
                      <locus target = "#81r"/> (rows of full-stop symbol above and below two lines made up of alternating red and black dots)
