                          <locus target = "#56r #56v"/>
                          Prayer of <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ወልደ፡ መስቀል፡</foreign> for salvation with
                          the <term key ="Asmat"/> found in the <title ref = "LIT1295Dersan"/>
                          and the Hebrew letters found in Ps 118
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a4">
                        <desc type = "OwnershipNote">Note of ownership by <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ወልደ፡ መስቀል፡</foreign> and his wife <foreign xml:lang = "gez">ወለተ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</foreign>, <locus target = "#56r"/> and passim</desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id = "a5">
                        <desc>
                          Overlooked words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target = "#ir(ecto) #7v #10v #18r #44r #50r #"/>, etc.);
                          and overlooked lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target = "#1r #69r"/>);
                          and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target = "#5r"/>, line 19 and <locus target = "#15r"/>, line 2)
                        </desc>
                      </item>
